sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Student
    actor Staff
    actor Manager
    participant Wizard as samsApplicationWizard LWC
    participant Controller as SamsDashboardController
    participant Database as Salesforce Database

    Student->>Wizard: Complete steps & submit
    Wizard->>Controller: createQuickEnrollment(data)
    Note over Controller: Begins Database Transaction
    Controller->>Database: Insert Student__c record
    Note over Database: Generates Student ID (SAMS-YYYY-XXXX)
    Controller->>Database: Insert Application__c record
    Controller->>Database: Insert initial Payment__c record
    Note over Controller: Commits Transaction on success
    Controller-->>Wizard: Return success response
    Wizard-->>Student: Display Success Toast
    Note over Database: Record-Triggered Flows fire
    Database-->>Student: Send registration confirmation email
